<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>This page is blocked</title>
  <style>
    :root { color-scheme: light dark; }
    body { margin: 0; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; background: #0b1220; color: #eef4ff; }
    main { max-width: 880px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 0 24px; }
    .card { border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.16); border-radius: 18px; background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255,255,255,.10), rgba(255,255,255,.045)); box-shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(0,0,0,.38); overflow: hidden; }
    .hero { padding: 30px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12); }
    .eyebrow { display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 14px; padding: 6px 10px; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(122,162,255,.18); color: #bcd0ff; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .04em; text-transform: uppercase; }
    h1 { margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 44px); line-height: 1.05; }
    p { line-height: 1.55; }
    .lead { color: rgba(238,244,255,.82); font-size: 18px; margin: 0; }
    .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 14px; padding: 24px 30px; }
    .item { border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10); border-radius: 14px; padding: 14px; background: rgba(0,0,0,.16); }
    .label { display: block; color: rgba(238,244,255,.58); font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    code, .value { overflow-wrap: anywhere; font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace; color: #ffffff; }
    .user { margin: 24px 30px 0; padding: 18px; border-left: 4px solid #34d399; border-radius: 12px; background: rgba(52,211,153,.13); }
    .user strong { color: #bbf7d0; }
    form.request { margin: 24px 30px; padding: 18px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12); border-radius: 14px; background: rgba(0,0,0,.16); }
    textarea { display: block; box-sizing: border-box; width: auto; min-height: 90px; border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.18); background: rgba(255,255,255,.08); color: #fff; padding: 10px; }
    button { margin-top: 10px; border: 0; border-radius: 999px; padding: 10px 16px; font-weight: 700; background: #7aa2ff; color: #071021; cursor: pointer; }
    .admin { margin: 0 30px 30px; padding: 18px; border-left: 4px solid #7aa2ff; border-radius: 12px; background: rgba(122,162,255,.10); }
    .diag { margin-top: 12px; color: rgba(238,244,255,.72); font-size: 13px; }
    .footer { padding: 18px 30px; color: rgba(238,244,255,.55); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10); font-size: 13px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<main>
  <section class="card" aria-labelledby="error-title">
    <div class="hero">
      <span class="eyebrow">Docker Proxy · Web Filtering</span>
      <h1 id="error-title">This page is blocked</h1>
      <p class="lead">Docker Proxy web filtering blocked this destination because it matched an enabled policy category.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="user">
      <strong>User guidance</strong>
      <p>This site is blocked by policy. Ask the proxy administrator to review it if needed.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid" aria-label="Request details">
      <div class="item"><span class="label">Requested URL</span><code>%U</code></div>
      <div class="item"><span class="label">Client address</span><span class="value">%i</span></div>
      <div class="item"><span class="label">Method and protocol</span><span class="value">%M · %P</span></div>
      <div class="item"><span class="label">Destination</span><span class="value">%H:%p</span></div>
      <div class="item"><span class="label">Proxy node</span><span class="value">%h</span></div>
      <div class="item"><span class="label">Event time UTC</span><span class="value">%T</span></div>
      <div class="item"><span class="label">Squid error</span><span class="value">%c</span></div>
      <div class="item"><span class="label">Elapsed</span><span class="value">%d seconds</span></div>
    </div>
    <form class="request" method="post" action="http://%h/policy-request">
      <strong>Request an exception</strong>
      <p>If this site is needed for legitimate work, send the details below to the proxy administrator.</p>
      <input type="hidden" name="block_type" value="webfilter">
      <input type="hidden" name="request_url" value="%U">
      <input type="hidden" name="client_ip" value="%i">
      <input type="hidden" name="domain" value="%H">
      <input type="hidden" name="destination" value="%H:%p">
      <input type="hidden" name="method" value="%M">
      <input type="hidden" name="squid_error" value="%c">
      <label for="user_note" class="label">Why should this be allowed?</label>
      <textarea id="user_note" name="user_note" maxlength="2000" placeholder="Briefly explain the business or household need."></textarea>
      <button type="submit">Submit request</button>
    </form>
    <div class="admin">
      <strong>Administrator guidance</strong>
      <p>Review selected web-filter categories, whitelist entries, and the matching web-filter block log.</p>
      <div class="diag">Diagnostic context: <span class="value">%x</span> · <span class="value">%D</span> <span class="value">%z</span> <span class="value">%E</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">If you believe this is incorrect, contact the proxy administrator: %w. Generated by %s.</div>
  </section>
</main>
</body>
</html>
